{"tid":860501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒「鳩行 > 鳩UP」，同唔同意？","createTime":"2018-10-13T11:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T12:39:32.000Z","uid":46849,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d08966302e312af78f6367944aa3ec63959e2d41","tid":860501,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:40:02.000Z","msg":"拿<br />\n唔好講咩含唔含淚<br />\n作為香港人<br />\n本身就已經含緊撚<br />\n而家只係睇你點樣用你既時間<br />\n<br />\n出黎鳩行<br />\n定係留係屋企鳩UP<br />\n自己揀<br />\n<br />\n幾廿歲人<br />\n驚俾人騎劫<br />\n驚俾人解散<br />\n驚俾人篤灰<br />\n驚俾人人鍊<br />\n咁多野驚<br />\n咪留返屋企打飛機囉<br />\n反正你呢種人<br />\n都係失敗過一次<br />\n就永遠失敗落去放棄架啦<br />\n等 free ride 囉<br />\n大把港豬同你一樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742b125b9058a367e80ab647fcfd3e7b1d368f6d","tid":860501,"uid":96465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"禁錯負皮 明天見"},{"pid":"a1d92a89269d5dfea2ff8281af73366f1b32db45","tid":860501,"uid":46849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"742b125b9058a367e80ab647fcfd3e7b1d368f6d","tid":860501,"uid":96465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:43:49.000Z","msg":"禁錯負皮 明天見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebe64facd05ecf7888e2e9601f7e283b6ef0c71","tid":860501,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}